Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World> Good Times*> Drumz> Morning Dew> Throwing Stones> Not Fade Away Encore Baby Blue

*Good Times without Bobby, Jerry, and Phil
